@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mfnrdk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.exp(tmp + 0.49) * 0.02))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.50) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.45)) * wp.exp(0.60))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v2) + 0.12)
    data[tid] = v0
